<br>
There are a number of solar sail designs, broken into two main classes, photonic and plasma driven (what you called &quot;magsail&quot;) such as the M2P2.<br>
<br>
The photonic has variants such as the reflector (which is a momentum mirror) and the radiator, which absorbs the photons and re-radiates them in the infra -red. <br>
<br>
Variants such as the M2P2 and the &quot;radiator&quot; have terrific performance potential.<br>
